 more fragmented."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"William Spayne was born about 1377, in Norfolk, England, United Kingdom. He had at least 1 daughter with Madre de Cicilie Spayne. He died in 1437, in Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America, at the age of 61."},"et":{"Abt 1377–1437":"umbes 1377–1437","1380–Female":"1380–Surnud","1403–1434":"1403–1434","1377–1437":"1377–1437","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1434":"1434","Abt 1377":"umbes 1377","1377":"1377","1380":"1380","Besthrope, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom","Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America":"Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Besthorpe, Norfolk, England":"Besthorpe, Norfolk, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"Abt 1377–1437":"noin 1377–1437","1380–Female":"1380–Kuollut","1403–1434":"1403–1434","1377–1437":"1377–1437","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1434":"1434","Abt 1377":"noin 1377","1377":"1377","1380":"1380","Besthrope, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America":"Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, England","Besthorpe, Norfolk, England":"Besthorpe, Norfolk, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"Abt 1377–1437":"environ 1377–1437","1380–Female":"1380–Décédée","1403–1434":"1403–1434","1377–1437":"1377–1437","1437":"1437","1403":"1403","1434":"1434","Abt 1377":"environ 1377","1377":"1377","1380":"1380","Besthrope, Norfolk, England, United Kingdom":"Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","Norfolk, Virginia, British Colonial America":"Norfolk, Virginie, Amérique coloniale britannique","Norfolk, England":"Norfolk, Angleterre","Besthorpe, Norfolk, England":"Besthorpe, Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"William Spayne est né environ 1377, à Norfolk, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni. Il a eu au moins 1 fille avec Madre de Cicilie Spayne. Il est décédé en 1437, à Norfolk, Virginie, Amérique colonia